{"tid":2388229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［宣誓風波］一名公務員拒絕宣誓並向老闆薦信辭職後竟獲得支持和祝福","createTime":"2021-01-31T03:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T04:47:13.000Z","uid":2547,"like":96,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f3ef9f5092adbddab4f5f04c52035684449034","tid":2388229,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:17:34.000Z","msg":"2021年一個放工後嘅傍晚，鼓起勇氣拎住封信去老闆房，老闆隔住口罩都望得出<br />\n「你做乜咁緊張？」<br />\n「係咩？我想辭職。」<br />\n「閂門入嚟再講。」<br />\n我地坐低左，我望一望手捏住封信<br />\n「我想講明，老闆同事都好好，想辭職唔係因為工作。」<br />\n「因為宣誓？」<br />\n我冇正面回答。<br />\n「我同屋企傾過，佢哋都支持。」<br />\n「之後有咩打算？」<br />\n「希望離開香港。」<br />\n<br />\n本來以為老闆會教訓我，簽個名啫，好為難你咩？點知⋯<br />\n<br />\n「平時你都唔多出聲，從來唔知你呢方面嘅想法。其實我哋老一輩唔係個個都一樣。只係屋企有老有嫩，有樓要供，心想嘅嘢有時要留返係心入面。」<br />\n「我知我好彩，冇乜家庭負擔。」<br />\n「襯後生，可以跟隨自己心意去做，就去做啦。」<br />\n冇想過會係咁真誠嘅對話中遞上我嘅辭職信<br />\n<br />\n留低係因為呢度係一個comfort zone<br />\n離開係因為呢度唔再係comfort zone<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/1140872419675207/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F492354117860377%2Fposts%2F1140872419675207%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=eb4dbc56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/1140872419675207/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a84655cc2539b61530a9ab96e74fae2fa2074378","tid":2388229,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10e59a96870311f873d66532fd901b4b3e938bc","tid":2388229,"uid":331838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:19:11.000Z","msg":"值得學習<br />\n鼓勵各位都應該咁做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f963dbe9e5af464067f51f63e0a79ea037ba7